FBIS4-14212 "drnes082_l_94007" FBIS-NES-94-082 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Knesset Defeats Bill To Fortify Golan Law Knesset Defeats Bill To Fortify Golan Law TA2704114194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1100 GMT 27 Apr 94 TA2704114194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] The proposed bill to fortify the Golan Law was defeated in the Knesset plenum by a majority of 57 to 47. Our correspondent Hayim Hecht reports that SHAS [Torah Observing Sephardim], Hayim Ramon, Shmu'el Avital, and Amir Peretz [members of Ramon's list to the Histadrut trade union elections] voted with the coalition.
